																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/09/26/democracy-kidnapped-madrid-police-fire-rubber-bullets-as-thousands-surround-spanish-congress-video-photos-rt/#respond" title="Comment on &#8216;Democracy kidnapped!&#8217; Madrid police fire rubber bullets as thousands surround Spanish Congress (VIDEO, PHOTOS)&nbsp;[RT]">Leave a comment</a></span>
